l.toArray.setIfInBounds i a  = (l.set i a).toArray := by
  apply ext'
  simp only [setIfInBounds]
  split
  · simp

theorem _root_.Array.mkArray_eq_toArray_replicate : mkArray n v = (List.replicate n v).toArray := by
  simp
